gov.sandia.cognition.math.matrix.custom

Class DenseMatrix.SVD

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.sandia.cognition.math.matrix.custom.DenseMatrix.SVD
  • Enclosing class:
    DenseMatrix

    public static final class DenseMatrix.SVD
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple container class for Singular Value Decomposition (SVD) results. Stores three matrices U, Sigma, and V as public members. NOTE: This includes V not V^T.
